@chenliang613 This PR is for supporting the Alluxio as a File System for supporting the CarbonFileFormat. Though there was a AlluxioCarbonFile in the past, this was failing with Alluxio. Since Alluxio does not inherit DistributedFileSystem, it has to be a AlluxioFileSystem that will be the change, as technically it does not support the appends on the File. Also, adopting to a AlluxioLock, however one can also use the ZookeeperLock, and also navigate.
